{
  "stem": "5228.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "She was watching me, that I don't talk, they shouldn't talk to us, or that-- or that I don't steal nothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "She was such a [? this-- ?] I was standing of my knees, and scrubbing the floor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And she was [INAUDIBLE] make laugh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They didn't look nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I mean, if this would happen today, it wouldn't be nothing by [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "This time, I just felt like animals, or that they kept us for animals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after this, I was working in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to take the peel-- the [INAUDIBLE] the potatoes, what I used to peel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The peels-- this I used to bring in the barrack, and give the girls to eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was even not washed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I couldn't-- didn't got [? water ?] to washing them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if they would see that I take them, they would beat me up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I just bring them inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they ate, like-- like they was something else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I couldn't bring even-- take for me nothing, but one bite.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because ?] then we was there how long it's come to the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's come to the end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when I'm going out from [INAUDIBLE] and work already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We was there [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was [? new boss. ?] He said he'd come just from America.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then he know from which side the American are coming, and from which side the Russian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he wanted to take us to the American side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, a lot that they killed in the last minute, or that he wanted to be a nice man, and come and shown that he has helped us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we survived because of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
